Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.62,0:02:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.89,0:03:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no one has ever fully explored it except for Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.86,0:03:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman Island located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates who are looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up in the turmoil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and involved in an all-out war!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.98,0:03:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Surume!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:04:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So you were doing everything he says in order to save your brother's life?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it your younger brother or older brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me try to save his life too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.84,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Gear 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:49.71,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"The Noah Closing in! Fishman Island Facing Destruction!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Ship of Promise! "Noah"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is it moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is doing it and how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bit strange, but why are you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a relic from history. It serves no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No! We can't let anything happen to that ship-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the proper day comes, no one is allowed to move that ship-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he took a lot of Energy Steroids and became a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We found Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... What do you three want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.69,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Surume!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.79,0:07:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Surume-sama, you are very strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect Wimpyhoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.34,0:07:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.94,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what Fishman Karate is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,His head is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it with a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not gonna work. Because I'm made of rubber!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Your skill is nothing compared to Jinbe's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.69,0:07:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! That's why you shouldn't depend on fake power!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.53,0:07:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Head; Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.23,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Iron Shell Squad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.63,0:08:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Your head's gonna crack open!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.52,0:08:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,His head was harder than iron!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.66,0:08:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Armament: Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.12,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.86,0:09:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't get hit at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.63,0:09:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Does he know when they come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing, Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.14,0:09:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Observation Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.11,0:09:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.13,0:09:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:10:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama, he is unbelievably strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's great! Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how strong the world-renowned pirate is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.75,0:10:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! I-Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.11,0:11:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Noah of the Fishman District?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is the Noah in the air over the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heading towards this plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost broken through the bubble around the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the bubble pops, the island is finished! We're all gonna get washed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,--What is that?! --The Noah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.87,0:11:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Super big!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the ship hits, the whole island will be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's operating it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it has an engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.31,0:12:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--What is that?! --It's gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know what's happening but we're all dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if the sea will turn red if we all get smashed at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.09,0:12:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say things like that! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,--Evacuate! --Get into the water off the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,F-Folks?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.22,0:12:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! I slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Wadatsumi - working for Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Vander Decken! I fell off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the ship! I don't wanna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.63,0:13:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Decken?! What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Hody, are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, is this one of your strategies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Decken is operating the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.01,0:13:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, you good-for-nothings!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.25,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.85,0:13:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.32,0:13:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,How tough can he be?! I attacked him with the Armament Haki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say Decken? That crazy pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not a part of the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.79,0:14:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept my love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you hear me, Shirahoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.79,0:15:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Decken threw the Noah like he threw those letters and axes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been loving you for 10 years since you were just a little kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.50,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one who could love you like I do in all the wide world!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my love! Love, love!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,L-O-V-E!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why can't you just accept it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.56,0:15:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Things that I throw with my Mark-Mark Fruit power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.56,0:15:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...won't stop until they crash into something or hit their target!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Noah the giant ship! It embodies my love for you! Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.41,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And drop dead along with all of Fishman Island, Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Decken! What about me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Wadatsumi! It's too late! It's impossible for me to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.44,0:16:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I need you to become a sacrifice upon Shirahoshi's death, along with the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it! The bubble is gonna pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We're doomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where did Princess Shirahoshi go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.56,0:16:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? She's not there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.73,0:16:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Princess! Princess Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Shirahoshi disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.44,0:17:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I am over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.74,0:17:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.20,0:17:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,--Princess Shirahoshi! --When did she go up there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wimpyhoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.74,0:17:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Mermaid Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.64,0:17:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi! Why did she do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.88,0:17:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that ship is flying towards her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Then she...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.53,0:18:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the girl that I love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.44,0:18:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you wanted to take just my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I am the only one who you want to kill, please do not harm the other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.39,0:18:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...of the Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,--Princess-sama! --Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The Noah is changing its course!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's heading towards Princess Shirahoshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.17,0:19:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do this, Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.78,0:19:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that crazy Decken bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.89,0:19:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He was gonna crush us all along with the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.33,0:19:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare he betray us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.57,0:19:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we do something to save her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.55,0:19:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How amazingly beautiful you are, Shirahoshi! Even your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.99,0:20:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to take the matter into your own hands
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to save the country, aren't you, Shirahoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.54,0:20:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Shira... hoshi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're eligible to become Vander Decken IX's wife as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You better die while you're still beautiful and live in my heart forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.82,0:20:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--Princess-sama! --How could you do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't do that! --Run, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn Wimpyhoshi! I told her to stick with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat! Captain Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where did Hody-san go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.35,0:21:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! He's up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He's heading for the Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess with me, Vander Decken!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like this idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.03,0:22:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard! How dare he hurt Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.10,0:22:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.53,0:22:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go up there! You stay here and take care of the plaza!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.94,0:22:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Luffy, the ship is in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.08,0:22:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think the ship is filled with water, Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know but I know Decken is a Devil Fruit user.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.18,0:22:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means there must be air for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.82,0:22:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a coral that produces bubbles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.56,0:22:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be counting on you to save my beloved Shirahoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.34,0:23:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.64,0:23:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.08,0:23:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Attempting to save Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirahoshi lures the Noah away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.85,0:23:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,After Luffy follows her,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,he's cornered into an underwater battle at a severe disadvantage against Hody.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.46,0:23:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, Shirahoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.36,0:23:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to finish things!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.90,0:23:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Hurry up, Luffy! Shirahoshi's Life in Jeopardy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.84,0:23:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
